node.text:
The question is HOW. How can you become a millionaire and create the success you’ve always wanted? If you want to learn how, read this short 1 min caption 👇

The MAIN reason people don’t change is because our brain is designed in a way to keep us safe. Keep us in the KNOWN. Or in other words, our comfort zone.

That’s why most children will grow up to have similar economic status to their parents.

Will probably live in the same neighborhood. And will probably hang with the same people they grew up with, simply because they grew up together. Not because they have similar interests, goals or visions.

The good thing is - it doesn’t have to apply to YOU. Most people are not everyone. There are people who choose to live differently. Who choose to create success in all areas of their lives.

How are they doing it? They force their mind to get out of the “familiar and known” and find people who have accomplished what they want to achieve in life.

Simply by surrounding yourself with the right people you can change your life direction.

That’s why today I highly recommend you follow some of the best mentors on Instagram, I will list them below:

Many people would like to turn Instagram into a full-time income, yet only a few are aware of how much it actually takes.

I've been a full-time Instagram marketer since 2018 and know all the tricks. The classic way to hit the 6-figure mark with IG looks like this:

1. You start a niche page
2. Post decent content daily
3. Gain momentum & maintain it
4. Become an expert in field "X"
5. Find a competitive edge
6. Develop a digital product
7. Build a website
8. Launch your product
9. Drive traffic
10. Scale

This approach bears many problems.

1. Most IG entrepreneurs still rely on the algorithm which is futile as it's not a sustainable traffic source
2. You can't become an expert overnight, it usually takes years
3. Niche pages have a very high trust barrier as you're "anonymous" & become more and more saturated
4. You have to take care of everything from "building the entire business fundament" to marketing & sales.

Not everyone has the equipment, skill, experience & perseverance to build out every aspect of a solid & sustainable business!

I sold tons of digital products & services within the past years & started to overwork myself, so I began to look for loopholes...with success!

Instead of doing everything by myself, I started working with high-ticket clients, such as course creators, consultants, coaches & similar and simply helped them build their fanbase via influencer- & content marketing AND sell their existing products.

I didn't have to be an expert, develop an in demand product, build complex sales funnels etc.

I just had to buy influencer shoutouts, outsource the content creation & hire a commission based closer to sell the products.

The best thing is: I still charge them $1,500-$2,000/mo + 30-40% profit share! This was an absolute GAME CHANGER for me. Instead of focusing on 10 different things, I'd focus on +/-3 AND make more money with just a handful of clients!

Wanna learn how to do the same? Follow 👉 @Igagencysecrets & let me teach you how its done!
